{"tid":1906523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家囑分時段午膳 「快食勿談話」","createTime":"2020-03-02T04:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T04:28:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a660c4ef073ec7e33b385ad632a2da1d49dedb51","tid":1906523,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200302/CCKUL2U3S6D2NCHUOFNCHOEGUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2FCCKUL2U3S6D2NCHUOFNCHOEGUQ%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=9af8dd55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2FCCKUL2U3S6D2NCHUOFNCHOEGUQ%2F&h=8daec505\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200302/CCKUL2U3S6D2NCHUOFNCHOEGUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n專家囑分時段午膳 「快食勿談話」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200302/large/1583079327_d27e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583079327_d27e.gif&h=16930f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】公務員今日起逐步復工，私營機構亦有跟隨。專家提示，疫情仍未見頂，打工仔在辦公室內都要戴口罩，共用電話、水機等更是辦公室傳播陷阱。專家建議僱主安排彈性上、下班及食飯時間，僱員宜自備午膳獨食，若選擇到餐廳用餐，避免對坐，令飛沫可集中向同一方向。衞生署專家則籲上班族用膳要快、要靜。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院長、公共衞生學院講座教授梁卓偉呼籲，僱主需為員工設想，採取彈性下班時間，盡量分散人流。中午用膳亦可分時段安排，辦公室座位盡量分隔多點空間，開窗引入鮮風。梁卓偉又籲打工仔減少共晉午膳，最好自攜「住家飯」。<br />\n<br />\n至於餐廳食肆，他建議應減少用圓枱，食客亦不要對坐，「多啲揀長方形嘅枱，而長方形嘅枱，大家就唔好對住坐，即使有飛沫，大家都同一個方向，唔會對住對方」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話及水機屬傳播陷阱<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疑曾染病 公主號兩港客有抗體<br />\n<br />\n醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超（圖）指出，現時群組個案主要有三大特徵，包括群眾聚集、脫口罩及使用公共設施，染病來源主要是飛沫和公用物件污染後的接觸傳播，復工防疫也可從以上三點入手，減低風險。除了戴口罩，梁子超建議上班族用膳時最理想是獨自進食或隔一至兩米距離，吃飯時不要談話減少飛沫傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君亦形容食飯是高危因素，除了「獨食」，亦要盡快吃，「可能多人聚集，大家都戴唔到口罩，可以諗吓帶飯或者叫外賣、拓開啲時間去食，食嗰陣盡快，去冇咁多人地方」。感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷則提示，共用電話、飲水機、影印機、門柄、燈掣、廁所廁紙、吹風機等都是辦公室傳播陷阱，室內謹記戴口罩、勤清潔或自備紙巾等個人物件。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧文烈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200302/large/1583079326_7bc8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583079326_7bc8.gif&h=72d01d07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fb71b3d9d6b1244ba2dc7341dd95ea4ffc588c2","tid":1906523,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"準備大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91349c2b4a867c0c2bb61a951c503d15abb46aeb","tid":1906523,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"食飯都要快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6917db4bd5dfa9039541c97dee9fcf88aac65009","tid":1906523,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"bc2663b67800081eb8d8a2eb4208eaf02e9041a4","tid":1906523,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"個專家係咪弱智<br />\n如果真係有人係傳播源 坐圓枱長枱有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a3677dce16ac300440548bc45d46a5bea091e6","tid":1906523,"uid":160662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:17:44.000Z","msg":"上星期經過D茶記<br />\n四人卡位五人坐, D 口水真係好味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950b6bd36e24dbf67c041ec57bb7c7d9ca476fd3","tid":1906523,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"遲D可能有專家話<br />\n應取消午膳時間"},{"pid":"aa7a5ead1d098981b11ad3e0e0acfa800398848d","tid":1906523,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2663b67800081eb8d8a2eb4208eaf02e9041a4","tid":1906523,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"個專家係咪弱智<br />\n如果真係有人係傳播源 坐圓枱長枱有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"長枱都唔好坐對面佢話<br />\n即係四人枱坐兩個平排好嘞<br />\n老闆心諗屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35896b0d41d0da17cf21c1149ceabf2acec59b3","tid":1906523,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"搭車同食飯都應該好似日本車廂咁唔好講野"},{"pid":"b31b4cd91944d721e690bf9309eaf5b3926f4129","tid":1906523,"uid":187957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"令飛沫可集中向同一方向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5db19e671c9287a71b91d784941a06590abb8c","tid":1906523,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"950b6bd36e24dbf67c041ec57bb7c7d9ca476fd3","tid":1906523,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"遲D可能有專家話<br />\n應取消午膳時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"做完9小時放工先食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上班前應該大量進食減低風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaf9828c692683b78275307e5439a27bc896c36","tid":1906523,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"on9個胃仲傷"},{"pid":"4c8b0b4a0f7ac9302bc68f2091ad8f75825c6a60","tid":1906523,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s